}}Frédéric François Chopin kɛna soo luɖu nɛ wendu luɖu sɔsɔ nɔɔyʋ. Ɛkɛ ɖɔɖɔ piyano maɖʋ sɔsɔ siŋŋ. Ɛ-[[piyaanoo]] mabʋ wɛ camɩyɛ kpem welesuu taa. E-liɖe lɩna [[Fransɩɩ|Fransɩ]] nɛ [[Pɔlɔɔñɩ]] pa-ajɛɛ taa.  

