Palʊla Frédéric François Chopin kɛ  Lakɩŋ fenaɣ kacalaɣ wiye, pɩnaɣ 1810 kɛ Farsoovii tɛtʊ taa, Polɔñ ɛjaɖɛ taa. Ɛkɛ cɩmɩŋ, keɣsi nɛ wendu luɖu sɔsɔ nɔɔyʋ. Ɛkɛ  ɖɔɖɔ piyano nɛ soo ndɩ ndɩ  maɖʋ sɔsɔ siŋŋ. E-liɖe lɩna Fransɩ nɛ Pɔlɔɔñɩ pa-ajɛɛ taa. Ɛ-wɩlɩyaa sɔsa kɔyɔ: Václav Würfel nɛ Józef Elsner piyele e-sukuli piya taa kɔyɔ:  Georges Mathias, Karol Mikuli nɛ Thomas Tellefsen. 

[[File:Frederic Chopin - Nocturne Eb major Opus 9, number 2.ogg|thumb|Frederic Chopin - Nocturne Eb major Opus 9, number 2]]

Payaɣ ɛ-caa se Nicolas Chopin nɛ e-ɖoo kɔyɔ Justyna Krzyzanowska. Ɛ-kɔɔ kɔyɔ Ludwika Jędrzejewicz.  Ɛtɛma ɛ-cɩmɩŋ nɛ e-piyano kpɛlɛkʊ ɛlɛ, ewolo Fransɩ ɛjaɖɛ. Peeɖe ɛkada ŋgbɛndʊ nɔɔyʊ, George Sand nɛ ɛna-ɩ pɛwɛ pɩnzɩ nakʊ. Pɩnzɩ mɩnɩŋ XIX taa ɛwɛ cɩmɩŋ maɖa nɛ wendu teya mba pakɩlʊ cɩmɩŋ weyi ɛkɩlʊ ɛyaa seɣtu yɔ pa-taa. Halɩ nɛ sɔnɔ ɖɔɖɔ mbʊ yɔ, e-wendu ɖɩɩna ɛyaa yɔɔ kʊyɩnaʊ hele hele. Ɛsɩba pɩnaɣ 1849  taa kɛ Paarii, Fransɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa.

